comment:
* Utilities for parsing the intent data used to launch the UI activity.
 *
 * @hide

methods.name: public static CancelSelectionRequest extractCancelUiRequest(@NonNull Intent intent)
methods.comment:
* Attempts to extract a {@link CancelSelectionRequest} from the given intent; returns null
     * if not found.

methods.name: public static RequestInfo extractRequestInfo(@NonNull Intent intent)
methods.comment:
* Attempts to extract a {@link RequestInfo} from the given intent; returns null
     * if not found.

methods.name: public static List<GetCredentialProviderInfo> extractGetCredentialProviderInfoList(@NonNull Intent intent)
methods.comment:
* Attempts to extract the list of {@link GetCredentialProviderInfo} from the given intent;
     * returns an empty list if not found.

methods.name: public static List<CreateCredentialProviderInfo> extractCreateCredentialProviderInfoList(@NonNull Intent intent)
methods.comment:
* Attempts to extract the list of {@link CreateCredentialProviderInfo} from the given intent;
     * returns an empty list if not found.

methods.name: public static List<DisabledProviderInfo> extractDisabledProviderInfoList(@NonNull Intent intent)
methods.comment:
* Attempts to extract the list of {@link DisabledProviderInfo} from the given intent;
     * returns an empty list if not found.

methods.name: public static ResultReceiver extractResultReceiver(@NonNull Intent intent)
methods.comment:
* Attempts to extract a {@link android.os.ResultReceiver} from the given intent, which should
     * be used to send back UI results; returns null if not found.

methodNames: public static CancelSelectionRequest extractCancelUiRequest(@NonNull Intent intent)
public static RequestInfo extractRequestInfo(@NonNull Intent intent)
public static List<DisabledProviderInfo> extractDisabledProviderInfoList(@NonNull Intent intent)
public static ResultReceiver extractResultReceiver(@NonNull Intent intent)
